Introduction

Yves is a South Korean singer and producer under PAIX PER MIL. She is a member of the girl group LOONA and the leader of its third sub-unit, yyxy. She made her solo debut on May 29, 2024, with EP "LOOP".

According to the LOONAverse, She lives in Eden along with Chuu, Go Won, and HyeJu (formerly known as Olivia Hye).
